INSERT INTO content (page, section, title, content, image_path) VALUES ('anouncement', 'main', 'Lycee S t Alexandre Sauli De Muhura Peres Barnabites', 'Lycee S t Alexandre Sauli De Muhura Peres Barnabites Home About Academic Staff Events Announcements Departments Fashion Design (FAD) Accounting ICT Software Development (SOD) Computer Systems & Architecture (CSA) Networking & Internet Technology (NIT) Contact Login Login Announcements Stay informed with the latest news, academic updates, events, and educational resources at Lycee de Muhura. Check back often to never miss an important update! New Academic Curriculum 2025 We are excited to announce the updated curriculum for the next academic year. It includes enhanced ICT programs, modern teaching methods, and skill-based learning opportunities for students. Read More Scholarship Opportunities Lycee de Muhura proudly introduces new scholarship programs for outstanding students. Apply before the deadline to secure funding for your education and skill development. Read More ICT Workshop for Students A week-long ICT workshop will be conducted to enhance practical skills in software development, networking, and system architecture. Open for all students interested in technology. Read More Annual Science Fair Our Annual Science Fair will showcase innovative projects from students across all departments. Join us to explore cutting-edge experiments, inventions, and creative learning ideas. Read More Fashion Design Showcase Our Fashion Design students will present their latest creations in a public showcase. Witness creativity, innovation, and professional craftsmanship in the world of fashion. Read More Parent-Teacher Meeting Scheduled for next month, this meeting allows parents to engage directly with teachers about student progress, curriculum updates, and strategies to improve learning outcomes. Read More Library Expansion Our school library has expanded with new books, digital resources, and study zones. Students can now access more learning material than ever before for academic excellence. Read More Upcoming Sports Events Prepare for an exciting series of inter-school sports competitions. Lycee de Muhura encourages students to participate and showcase their athletic skills. Read More Developers IRASUBIZA Jean Cadeau IHIRWE Aimee Saina HABAKUBAHO Brainy Justin TUMURAMYWE Placide Email: lycemuhur@gmail.com School Location Rwanda, Eastern Province Gatsibo District Muhura Sector, Taba Cell Kanyinya Village Follow Us © 2025 LYCEE SAINT ALEXANDRE SAULI DE MUHURA — All Rights Reserved', NULL);
